<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Template</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .content {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Welcome, {{name}}!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Thank you for using our service. Here is your important information.</p>
            <p>If you requested a dynamic link, click below:</p>
            <p><a href="{{url}}" style="display:inline-block; padding:10px 20px; background:#007BFF; color:#fff; text-decoration:none; border-radius:4px;">Action Link</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Sanad API. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
